items.text: Enjoyed TeoChew Fishball 潮洲鱼丸

Having Song Chew Lor Mee, guess that's where my dad always buy me for bf! Try it!

Mee sua - Taiwan style. Western food - corner stall

Seng kee mee suah is terrrrific!

Best wu Xiang !

try Quan Xing Spicy Prawn Cracker #01-25 (Chinese rojak )
Bbq chicken wing's gooood!

Yummy Nasi Lemak stall here - go for Aliff Nasi Lemak

Morning : Nasi Lemak or Fish Soup .. Night: Mee sua

U will like the food at there

bar chor mee : shiok!

I feel so tired. Oh wait, everyday I feel tired -.-

the pisang goreng vy cripy n yummy

so missing thereT^T
